name: Kubu Kapas Bali
address: Jl. Raya Mambal Semana, Mambal, Kec. Abiansemal, Kabupaten Badung, Bali 80352, Indonesia
review 1: Absolutely amazing stay, very attentive and caring hosts! Came and cleaned every day! Let us check out late too which we appreciated very much! Highly recommend a stay here! Beds are super comfy too!
review 2: Gorgous 4 bedroom private villa in Mambal Village just out of Ubud.  (You can rent 1, 2, 3 or 4 bedrooms & all priced accordingly).  Great pool.  Set in the middle of Rice Terraces.  Breakfast is included your price.  Cooking facilities in kitchen or you can have Gojek deliveries.  We also had massages in the villa that Wayan the host can organise for you.  Laundry & transport service also available.  We highly recommend.
review 3:
Villa Kubu Kapas Bali

This newly built villa with annex in the Abiansemal district offers their guests an oasis of peace and relaxation in the middle of nature.
You reach the the Villa via a paved private path. The property is equipped with a pool and its own drinking water supply.
The main building has four bedrooms, a bathroom with shower and bathtub and a large living/dining area. All rooms are airconditioned.
A covered open kitchen and another bathroom with shower in the annex near the pool complete the offer.

The hostfamily gave us a very warm welcome and offered us an extraordinary hospitality.
A traditional breakfast is included.

Transportation with car and scooters can be arranged for fair prices. An airport pick you up service can also be arranged.

This property is particularly suitable for families with children or couples who want to enjoy their vacation away from the major tourist centers in Bali.

Attractions include the nearby Taman Ayun Temple, the Sangeh Monkey Forest and the Ubud Palace.

Nearby popular leisure activities for the whole family are the Telaga Waja Rafting and Elephant Ride Packages.
